{"type":"tool_start","tool":"memory_store","tool_use_id":"call_0505a5923c6d42b88a6d3153","input_preview":"{\"key\": \"nullalis-product-overview\", \"content\": \"Nova is the founder of nullalis, a personal second-brain product for individual high-agency users. Architecture: cell-pod isolation per user, Postgres-canonical storage, pgvector for embeddings, typed-edge graph layer with bi-temporal correctness (adopted from Graphiti), communities via label-propagation (LPA). The 12 V-infinity pillars: continuous presence, composing memory, proactive with restraint, cell-pod multi-agent, visual ingestion, ambient voice, approval as product surface, connector depth, portability, self-improvement on a leash, end-user defensibility, open ecosystem on consent.\", \"category\": \"core\", \"scope\": \"global\"}","run_id":"r-1777921057284-1"}
